{
  "stem": "4963.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, the house was quite large.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there were different families living in the same house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But perhaps we lived at the time in two, three rooms.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My Uncle Osher was also quite a survivor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was, as we used to call him, [NON-ENGLISH], he knew the land of the-- the, the layout of the land.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he would always [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] accommodate us with whatever [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] better-- we were really, I would say, more privileged than other people.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So as I recall, we never were hungry for basic food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he was an administrator.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he knew-- he was also a very good public relations person.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was his forte.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was very vocal, and he was very articulate and learned.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I would say my whole family was really-- learning was one of the-- studies were, were, was one of the backbone of our family, really.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My mother was already a college graduate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My father was a college graduate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My uncle was a doctor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was-- I think everyone in my family was, you know, educated, had higher education.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My aunt was sent to Paris to study because she was always very arty, and they wanted her to-- I remember my grandmother saying that she was a very beautiful lady, and I would always admire her.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She would come from Paris with suitcases with all the latest clothing and everything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But my, my, my grandmother always groomed her to be a princess.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She never says, oh, you don't have to put your hands in the, in the, in any water, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You'll have servants, which, incidentally, that's how I was brought up, too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We were not even permitted to dress ourselves until age-- I can't even remember.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
